		Learn more ----https://t.co/OBwH8eUxQv pic.twitter.com/sRZ3nYbOLV Tunisia and Uruguay were among the big movers as they entered the top 20 while the matches in Asia helped Oman, Chinese Taipei and Philippines improve their rankings. FIFA's newest members Kosovo, who climbed 24 spots to 152nd, and Gibraltar, who leapt 10 spots to 196th, also benefited from friendly victories. Top 10 rankings: 1. Germany 2. Brazil 3. Belgium 4. Portugal 5. Argentina 6. Switzerland 7. France 8. Spain 9. Chile 10. Poland Reuters